            <title>联想 2024 款拯救者 R9000P 笔记本新增“锐龙 9 7945HX + 16G + 1T + RTX4070”版售 10499 元起</title>
            <link>https://www.ithome.com/0/805/528.htm</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.ithome.com/0/805/528.htm</guid>
            <pubDate></pubDate>
            <updated>Sun, 27 Oct 2024 01:31:20 GMT</updated>
                
                
            <content:encoded>
                <![CDATA[
                    
                    <div class="tougao-user">感谢IT之家网友 <a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D2118746" rel="nofollow">寒雨111</a> 的线索投递！</div>
            <p><a class="s_tag" href="https://www.ithome.com/" target="_blank">IT之家</a> 10 月 27 日消息，联想现已为 2024&nbsp;款拯救者&nbsp;R9000P&nbsp;笔记本推出“锐龙&nbsp;9 7945HX + 16GB RAM + 1TB SSD + RTX4070”显卡配置，可选黑白双色，<strong>其中黑色售价为&nbsp;10499&nbsp;元，白色为&nbsp;10799&nbsp;元</strong>，两款笔记本均将于&nbsp;10&nbsp;月&nbsp;31&nbsp;日&nbsp;20:00&nbsp;开售。</p><dir><a contenteditable="false" href="https://u.jd.com/KrwRcMj" target="_blank"><span class="card main-site"><span class="card-logo"><img height="800" src="https://img14.360buyimg.com/pop/jfs/t1/232992/4/27439/132197/670c9abaFbc0f8c36/474bde4256b35af9.jpg" title="联想 2024 款拯救者 R9000P 笔记本新增“锐龙 9 7945HX + 16G + 1T + RTX4070”版售 10499 元起" width="800" /></span><span class="card-info"><span class="card-title"><span class="mall-data">京东</span><span class="card-name">“锐龙 9 7945HX + 16GB RAM + 1TB SSD + RTX4070</span></span><span class="card-abstract">RTX 4070 版本</span><span class="card-controls"><span class="price"> 10499 元起</span><span class="card-btn-deep">直达链接</span></span></span></span></a></dir><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="940" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/10/f55e048c-8a94-4b66-a6c1-c3466e00e28d.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="联想 2024 款拯救者 R9000P 笔记本新增“锐龙 9 7945HX + 16G + 1T + RTX4070”版售 10499 元起" width="746" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1358" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/10/d5993115-f55d-459f-9cda-b3e750cfaa07.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="联想 2024 款拯救者 R9000P 笔记本新增“锐龙 9 7945HX + 16G + 1T + RTX4070”版售 10499 元起" width="746" /></p><p>外观方面，系列笔记本采用电竞风格设计，配备 120x75mm&nbsp;一体式精准触摸板、LEGION TrueStrike&nbsp;原感键盘。</p><p>该机搭载&nbsp;16&nbsp;核心&nbsp;32&nbsp;线程 AMD&nbsp;锐龙&nbsp;9 7945HX&nbsp;处理器，配备&nbsp;16GB DDR5 5200MHz&nbsp;RAM&nbsp;及&nbsp;1TB PCle 4.0&nbsp;固态硬盘，使用&nbsp;140W RTX4070&nbsp;显卡，采用了霜刃&nbsp;Pro&nbsp;散热系统&nbsp;5.0，整机性能释放可达&nbsp;200W（IT之家注：CPU&nbsp;及&nbsp;GPU&nbsp;分别可达为&nbsp;100W、140W），支持独显直连。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1274" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/10/fa658260-7ed8-4b63-894b-ad69871063ed.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="联想 2024 款拯救者 R9000P 笔记本新增“锐龙 9 7945HX + 16G + 1T + RTX4070”版售 10499 元起" width="738" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="984" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/10/3b44a640-b7d4-451a-9bee-19ab548e8281.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="联想 2024 款拯救者 R9000P 笔记本新增“锐龙 9 7945HX + 16G + 1T + RTX4070”版售 10499 元起" width="742" /></p><p>该机配备一块&nbsp;2560x1440&nbsp;分辨率&nbsp;240Hz&nbsp;面板，亮度&nbsp;500&nbsp;尼特，响应速度&nbsp;3ms，支持&nbsp;10-Bit&nbsp;色彩（8-Bit + FRC），覆盖 100% DCI-P3&nbsp;色域。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1016" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/10/98426cf0-2ae3-4f08-aef7-aa2552d1036a.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="联想 2024 款拯救者 R9000P 笔记本新增“锐龙 9 7945HX + 16G + 1T + RTX4070”版售 10499 元起" width="744" /></p><p>此外，该机采用 80Wh&nbsp;电池，支持&nbsp;140W USB-C&nbsp;便捷快充以及&nbsp;300W PC&nbsp;快充，支持&nbsp;Wi-Fi 6E&nbsp;技术；机身左置&nbsp;1&nbsp;个&nbsp;USB-A 3.2 Gen 1&nbsp;接口、1&nbsp;个&nbsp;USB-C 3.2 Gen 2&nbsp;接口；机身右置&nbsp;1&nbsp;个&nbsp;USB-A 3.2 Gen 1&nbsp;接口、1&nbsp;个&nbsp;3.5mm&nbsp;音频接口；机身后置&nbsp;1&nbsp;个&nbsp;RJ45&nbsp;接口、1&nbsp;个 USB-C 3.2 Gen 2&nbsp;接口、1&nbsp;个 HDMI 2.1&nbsp;接口、2&nbsp;个 USB-A 3.2 Gen 1&nbsp;接口。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="960" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/10/ccaee8e8-dce4-4a7f-b949-f4f7db4411c6.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="联想 2024 款拯救者 R9000P 笔记本新增“锐龙 9 7945HX + 16G + 1T + RTX4070”版售 10499 元起" width="738" /></p><p>2024 年 11.11 大促全网好价合集：<a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fcontentlist%3Fapi%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fnapi.ithome.com%252Fapi%252Ftopmenu%252Fgetmenufeeds%252F166%252F0%252Fnone%252F0%26title%3D2024%25E5%258F%258C11%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25BF%2583%25E7%25B2%25BE%25E9%2580%2589%26mode%3D0" target="_blank" title="点此查看">点此查看</a></p><p><span class="font-color-red"><strong>京东无